'''Maisie''' is a mentioned character in ''Genshin Impact''. She was first mentioned in the [[On the Trail of Behemoths]] event. 

==Profile==
[[Helka]] refers to Maisie as a timid girl and says that her constitution is too frail. She currently lives in [[Nasha Town]].
